# Caulking Shed — Illustration Prompt

Create a richly detailed, roughly square digital painting sized to sit beside narrative text on desktop or mobile screens. Depict a grounded late-medieval harbor campaign setting with tar smoke, oakum, caulking irons, seam work, and blackened boards. Emphasize crisp readability, brighter maritime color accents, and clear spatial separation more than muddy painterly atmosphere.

- Composition: smoky shed interior with benches, buckets, and a route back toward the storehouse lanes.
- Key elements: oakum twists, seam tools, tar pots, scorched timber, and practical fix-up clutter.
- Character focus: caulkers who see their contribution as obviously minor despite it stopping departure.
- Navigation hint: show a clear way back toward Salt Storehouse and the main harbor path.

